Unable to reproduce - this indicates a subclass of RelaunchLastAction is not implementing the required method #getText() - all subclasses in the SDK implement this method. Perhaps you are using other plug-ins? or your install is corrupt?

Getting similar message. This is neither a clean Eclipse-only installation, but has a lot of other stuff installed, e.g. BIRT, EMF etc.

In my case, the previous error shows probably the originating plugin: "Could not create action delegate for id: com.mountainminds.eclemma.ui.actions.CoverageLast"

However, it would be good to have a more informative Exception in the RelaunchLastAction to better find the cause of the problem, e.g. the class name of the Launch implementation or the bundle name.
